            <title><![CDATA[【[拳头]拒绝暴力！#语言暴力精神暴力都是家暴#】#一定要知道的9个家暴真相#：①家暴只有零次和无数次；②语言暴力也是暴力；③家暴与学历、职业等无关；④一味...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[拳头]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/h_quantou-81f684d5ed.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>拒绝暴力！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%AE%B6%E6%9A%B4%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%AE%B6%E6%9A%B4%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#语言暴力精神暴力都是家暴#</span></a>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E8%A6%81%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E7%9A%849%E4%B8%AA%E5%AE%B6%E6%9A%B4%E7%9C%9F%E7%9B%B8%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E8%A6%81%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E7%9A%849%E4%B8%AA%E5%AE%B6%E6%9A%B4%E7%9C%9F%E7%9B%B8%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#一定要知道的9个家暴真相#</span></a>：①家暴只有零次和无数次；②语言暴力也是暴力；③家暴与学历、职业等无关；④一味隐忍只会纵容家暴；⑤家暴不是“家务事”……今天是国际<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B6%88%E9%99%A4%E9%92%88%E5%AF%B9%E5%A6%87%E5%A5%B3%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E6%97%A5%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B6%88%E9%99%A4%E9%92%88%E5%AF%B9%E5%A6%87%E5%A5%B3%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E6%97%A5%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#消除针对妇女暴力日#</span></a>，如遇家暴，请勇敢地用法律保护自己，向一切家庭暴力说“不”👇🏻（央视新闻）<img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hk785lred8j20u01hc493.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hk785lna4hj20u01hcafn.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hk785liiljj20u01hcdiv.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hk785lnho6j20u01hcgqn.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hk785lpac9j20u01hctes.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hk785lqdz3j20u01hcjya.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hk785lpl05j20u01hcafy.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hk785lpmioj20u01hcte7.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hk785ls40sj20u01hcaho.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
